[h3 id=Rationale 
	" Rationale
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"By using an open license, content is able to be contributed by many users and worked on as a team.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Ramifications 
	" Ramifications
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"It is important to note that the site license is the same as, or similar to, ones used by many other sites. If TASVideos used a more restrictive license, we'd be unable to, for example, upload videos to YouTube, which offers to host videos under the same 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.youtube.com/t/creative_commons/ rel=nofollow 
		"Creative Commons license
	]a
	" or under one 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.youtube.com/t/terms rel=nofollow 
		"very similar
	]a
	" to it. With such unencumbered licensing, we are able to publish videos submitted here to YouTube and many others for hosting.
]div
